# ⚙️ Instalação

## 1. Clonar o projeto

```bash
git clone https://github.com/SEU_USERNAME/hotel-python-palace.git
```

---

## 2. Entrar na pasta

```bash
cd hotel-python-palace
```

---

## 3. Criar ambiente virtual

### Windows

```powershell
python -m venv venv
venv\Scripts\activate
```

### Linux

```bash
python3 -m venv venv
source venv/bin/activate
```

---

## 4. Instalar dependências

```bash
pip install -r requirements.txt
```

---

# ▶️ Executar Aplicação Flask

```bash
python app.py
```

Abrir:

```txt
http://127.0.0.1:5000
```

---

# 💻 Executar Aplicação Java Swing

Entrar na pasta:

```txt
swing/
```

Executar:

```txt
executar_dashboard.bat
```

ou:

```bash
javac -cp ".;lib/sqlite-jdbc.jar" *.java

java -cp ".;lib/sqlite-jdbc.jar" HotelPythonPalaceDashboard
```

